Download TIGER shapes for Area Landmarks

Source: R/area_landmarks.R
tt_area_landmarks.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Area Landmarks

Usage

tt_area_landmarks(state, year = 2021)

Arguments

state

FIPs, postal codes, or full name of states.

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_area_landmarks('DE')
